Java based website and create github workflow::
1.Create Java Project java-ci-projec->pom.xml->src folder->main folder->java folder->java (hello.java ) file.
public class Hello 
{
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        System.out.println("Build Successful");
    }
}

pom.xml file:

<project xmlns="http://maven.apache.org/POM/4.0.0">
    <modelVersion>4.0.0</modelVersion>

    <groupId>com.example</groupId>
    <artifactId>java-ci</artifactId>
    <version>1.0</version>

    <build>
        <plugins>
            <plugin>
                <groupId>org.apache.maven.plugins</groupId>
                <artifactId>maven-compiler-plugin</artifactId>
                <version>3.8.1</version>
                <configuration>
                    <source>8</source>
                    <target>8</target>
                </configuration>
            </plugin>
        </plugins>
    </build>
</project>

Make a simple Maven project with pom.xml and Hello.java
Hello.java prints “Build Successful”
2.push code to git:
git init
git add .
git commit -m "Initial commit"
git branch -M main
git remote add origin <repo-url>
git push -u origin main
3.Add GitHub Actions
Create folder: .github/workflows(Inside your project, create a folder:.github/workflows,
Inside that folder, create a file named:maven-build.yml)
Create file: maven-build.yml

create .github folder in java-ci-project-> create wrokflows folder->inside create maven-build.yml text file.

in yml paste this:
name: Java Maven Build

on:
  push:
    branches:
      - main

jobs:
  build:
    runs-on: ubuntu-latest

    steps:
    - name: Checkout code
      uses: actions/checkout@v4

    - name: Set up Java
      uses: actions/setup-java@v4
      with:
        java-version: '8'
        distribution: 'temurin'

    - name: Build project
      run: mvn clean package


4.Configure Workflow:
name: Java Maven Build
on: push:
      branches: [main]
jobs:
  build:
    runs-on: ubuntu-latest
    steps:
    - uses: actions/checkout@v4
    - uses: actions/setup-java@v4
      with:
        java-version: '8'
        distribution: 'temurin'
    - run: mvn clean package

5.Push Workflow:
git add .github/workflows/maven-build.yml
git commit -m "Add workflow"
git push

if rejected: paste this :
git pull origin main --allow-unrelated-histories
git add .
git commit -m "Merge local with remote"
git push -u origin main
or just this:git push -u origin main --force

